    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-11-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-11-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="131" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d131">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Dun</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 22,
                            1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is reported that American and Canadian seal fishery vessels may be placed
                        under the Japanese flag next season. Comity will naturally counsel Japanese
                        Government to defeat any such attempted abuse of friendly flag to evade
                        results of Paris Arbitration.</p>
            </div>
